            <em>“The Metropolitan Museum of Art and the Nrityagram Dance Ensemble are both extraordinary and remarkable, by themselves on any ordinary day. Brought together by the World Music Institute, this one evening two-performances only show was a truly unique experience….. The Nrityagram Dance Ensemble at the Metropolitan Museum of Art's Temple of Dendur was like a priceless jewel cradled securely in a setting of the rarest enchanted metal.”</em>
