        <p>
            <em> “Like so much of Sen’s work, “Invoking Shiva” flexes a high level of skill without calling attention to it….. If you were busy marveling at the dancers, and not marveling at the craft, that may have been what Sen, and her assistant choreographer, Heshma Wignaraja from Chitrasena, wanted. Yet the remarkable fusion of nritta and abhinaya looked unlike almost any other Indian classical company we get to see.” </em>
